{"tid":1561041,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"咀嚼唔合口 我屌","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T09:29:56.000Z","uid":196699,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ed82c6c9b5e3f96291e443eb4480d0b3e1533d4b","tid":1561041,"uid":196699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:31:21.000Z","msg":"話說我呢一兩個星期同屋企人食飯 <br />\n佢完全食飯咀嚼係冇合口食 啲聲好嘈呀  <br />\n聽到頭有啲唔舒服 類似暈車嘅感覺 聽到燥燥地 <br />\n食嘢就開口咀嚼 我好撚困擾 次次食飯都好唔舒服<br />\n要食一陣坐一邊抖下 唔想聽咀嚼聲 我係咪有病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1a54be059d5ed217b211617d8e9947292542da","tid":1561041,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"8a8ab9fc7657ecd8326a350c947f9fde74f51f9d","tid":1561041,"uid":196699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fe1a54be059d5ed217b211617d8e9947292542da","tid":1561041,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:32:58.000Z","msg":"我政治中立 不過我會出去遊行 <br />\n藍絲仆街死"},{"pid":"8a948302933d35bd7c9a22a4f62fbe8007ea9a17","tid":1561041,"uid":226695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:33:38.000Z","msg":"咀嚼點解又會關政治立場事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8676099c2a2874c041833323bdbf185a8398de7","tid":1561041,"uid":208253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:34:41.000Z","msg":"【 五大訴求，缺一不可 】遊行公佈<br />\n<br />\n林鄭在日前正式宣佈撤回引渡條例，在立法會復會後，以不需表決的方式完全撤回引渡條例。有外國的朋友甚至對香港人致以「祝賀」，但緊接的周末，港人的抗爭依然不斷。<br />\n<br />\n因為我們知道，勝利仍未來臨。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭的撤回引渡條例修訂，僅是以退為進，將一條已死的條文再一次加以埋葬，自以為將風暴的起源堵上，風暴就會平息，就可以名正言順地污名化香港人的持續抗爭。我們要求正式撤回條例，並不是單純在行政程序上撤回，而是我們所追求的是一個負責任、會聆聽民意、會尊重民意的政府，因此我們不會接受一個為了自身一人的面子，玩弄文字，無視程序的政府管治。數月來，政府、警隊醜態原形畢露，林鄭想以虛假的「四大公關SHOW」回應五大訴求，簡直天荒夜談。<br />\n<br />\n在惡法撤回之後，我們必須清晰告訴世界，我們之所以繼續抗爭，是因為我們仍有四個訴求未被回應，而餘下的四個訴求，是彰顯我們對社會願景的原則，反映我們對生活的城市的愛，並且正面迎戰我們不能忍受的醜惡政權的種種惡行。<br />\n<br />\n我們不能忍受，警員濫暴濫權，變成持有合法武力的黑社會，而沒有任何獨立監察的制度可以制衡；<br />\n<br />\n我們不能忍受，守住香港，擋住惡法的年輕人一個又一個因為捨身行動而失去自由，被指控發動暴動，被指稱為暴徒、曱甴；<br />\n<br />\n我們不能忍受，我們的家人、朋友，每一個心愛的人生活在荒誕的極權的謊言之中，而我們手中沒有任何權力、選票可以與之抗衡；<br />\n<br />\n我們不能忍受以上種種，因此，為我們愛的城市，為了我們身邊的每一個人，我們會繼續抗爭，行使我們相信的方法繼續抗爭，直至五大訴求得到落實；直至我們心中公義、民主的社會來臨為止。<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油，萬事小心。<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊遊行詳情＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n2019年9月15日<br />\n下午2時30分<br />\n銅鑼灣東角道集合<br />\n遊行往中環遮打道<br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019年9月11日"},{"pid":"594af694f28ddaf3a5a67a5747f09547d21b412e","tid":1561041,"uid":196699,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8a948302933d35bd7c9a22a4f62fbe8007ea9a17","tid":1561041,"uid":226695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:33:38.000Z","msg":"咀嚼點解又會關政治立場事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:37:15.000Z","msg":"一次去親戚屋企食飯 佢不停屌香港示威者 <br />\n話朋友係7樓睇到有人派水比示威者遊行<br />\n又話佢朋友個仔去遊行有錢收<br />\n話人目光短淺 話中國政府為香港人好<br />\n屌曬所有藍絲 去仆街死<br />\n最尾補句我政治中立"},{"pid":"24676ca09939a1692ee287b9fc0411f7756db3ce","tid":1561041,"uid":84277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:43:01.000Z","msg":"1999......"},{"pid":"0391d868f5f9f4d0e8e4699829346d103b6e3409","tid":1561041,"uid":317609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:48:24.000Z","msg":"agger 最撚憎啲人食野食到jap jap聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117f804f068cf672eea43e89a54708626dd9d50f","tid":1561041,"uid":196699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0391d868f5f9f4d0e8e4699829346d103b6e3409","tid":1561041,"uid":317609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:48:24.000Z","msg":"agger 最撚憎啲人食野食到jap jap聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"聽到好煩燥呀"},{"pid":"525373d9885927837f993be603bc83a384e21ccd","tid":1561041,"uid":226695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:44:09.000Z","msg":"呢啲大是大非嘅議題上，我唔明點解有人仲會政治偽中立，不知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ceeb685eb943962ff6c9ee323853fef80038538","tid":1561041,"uid":135114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"仲有撩牙 jip jip聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8c7df64c74f4790c89ad0f94c4c8764bbf6179","tid":1